#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:93
msgid ""
"The new window is a fully functional window, which is part of the same "
"instance of Blender. This can be useful, e.g. if you have multiple "
"monitors."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:96
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A new window can be created from :menuselection:`View --> Duplicate Area "
"into new Window`."
msgstr ""
"Se puede crear una nueva ventana desde :menuselection:`Window (Ventana) "
"--> Duplicate Window (Duplicar ventana)`."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:98
msgid ""
"You can also create a new window from an existing area by :kbd:`Shift-"
"LMB` on the area splitter widget, then drag slightly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/areas.rst:101
